# The FastAPI bridge (api/) runs on a Hugging Face Space, not Vercel. Excluding
# it stops Vercel from auto-detecting a Python serverless function and bundling
# torch (which blows past the 500 MB function-size limit). In production /api/*
# is proxied to the Space via the rewrite in next.config.ts (API_BRIDGE_URL);
# api/ stays in the repo only for local dev (npm run dev:api).
api/
